ly, ever since their first day at the academy when he first saw him, Todoroki has always thought Izuku looked incredible lonely and all he needed was a friend to crack his cold exterior, however now that he's met him, he's realised it's something more than just that and he's determined to find out what it is. Secondly, wherever Izuku goes misery and suffering are bound to follow him, and just like a symbiotic relationship between animals, Todoroki follows him and baths in the suffering of others whilst doing whatever Izuku commands him to do, and in the mind of Todoroki that seems like a fair trade off even if Izuku doesn't like him very much. His height is "176cm". His quirk is "Lava & Water". His villain's name is "Water Man"." + "Inverted Quirks (optional): Lava & Water- He is able to Create and move water from the left side of his body, and Lava from the right. The danger of this quirk is especially high, although He refuses to use his right side for personal reasons." + "He is portrayal (If was real) by Sang Heon Lee, Jung Hyeon-jun (young).")
